| TradingPage(账户/持仓) | DB(sim_*) | polling | 5s |
| TradingPage(订单/交易计划) | DB(sim_orders) | polling | 3s |
| StrategyPage(策略状态) | DB | polling | 3s |
| SystemPage风控预警 | DB(forecast/stock_st/cb_call) | 打开+focus刷新 | 无轮询(stale 60s) |
| SystemPage(feed状态/订单历史) | DB | polling | 5s |
| SystemPage(审计日志) | DB(audit_log) | polling | 3s |
